snippet.textDisplay:
Hello dear Selena Gomez-community,



My concern is to help my best friend, who is currently in a difficult chapter of his life (he could tell you more about it himself 😀).



He is now 16 years old and will be 17 in 3 days and his dream has been to have a YouTube channel since he was 13 years old.


It may be a bit unrealistic and childish to ask for your help here, but I want to make it clear that this is not hypocrisy or anything, just an attempt to make my best friend's dream come true and help him in his situation.



Thank you very much for reading your concerns up to here and I wish you a pleasant day!



I link his YouTube channel where he already has 3400 subscribers here.



https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmznOwb6VVkIf-Pl4anywwg
